### 2025-12-14 — Obsidian Dataview Power 🔧

**Problem:** Need dynamic views of project status without manual updates

**Technique:** Use simple TABLE queries for 80% of use cases. Only upgrade to DataviewJS when calculations are needed.

**Example:**
```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link as "Note",
  dateformat(file.mtime, "yyyy-MM-dd") as "Updated"
FROM "folder"
SORT file.mtime DESC
LIMIT 10
```

**When to use:** Any time you need a dynamic list or table that updates automatically.

**Related:** [[Snippets/Dataview Query Library]]

